	"Whenever you reduce a humanoid to 0 hit points, you can use your reaction to attempt to trap their soul inside the bracer. The target must succeed on a DC 15 Wisdom saving throw; a creature can choose to fail this saving throw if it wishes. On a successful save its soul departs as normal. On a failed save, its soul is trapped within the bracer. If the creature is wearing any items meant to trap or redirect its soul after death, such as a {@item ring of mind shielding}, the bracer fails. A creature whose soul is trapped in the bracer can only be restored to life by a {@spell wish} spell, which removes the soul from the bracer.": "每当你把一个人形生物减少到0点生命值时，你可以用你的反应来尝试把他们的灵魂困在手镯里。目标必须在DC15智慧救赎中成功；如果生物愿意，它可以选择不做这个救赎。如果救赎成功，它的灵魂会如常离开。如果救赎失败，它的灵魂就会被困在手镯里。如果该生物穿戴了任何旨在困住或引导其死后灵魂的物品，比如（%0%），那么手镯就会失效。灵魂被困在手镯中的生物只能通过{@spell wish}的法术恢复生命，将灵魂从手镯中移除。",
	"While the bracer contains a soul, you use an action to take on the appearance of the body the soul belonged to, as if you had cast the {@spell alter self} spell. While transformed, you can cast the detect thoughts spell from the bracer at will but can target only the soul when you do so. The transformation lasts for a maximum duration of 1 hour, after which you revert to your regular form. The transformation also ends if you take off the bracer. This property of the bracer can't be used again until the next dawn.": "当手镯里有一个灵魂时，你会使用一个动作来呈现出灵魂所属身体的样子，就像你施展了（%0%）法术一样。在变身时，你可以随意从手镯中施展侦测思想的法术，但在施展时只能针对灵魂。变身持续的时间最长为1小时，之后你会恢复到你的正常形态。如果你摘下手镯，这种转变也会结束。手环的这一属性在下一个黎明前不能再次使用。"
